  "description": "Amalgamation of two adjoining ground floor flats into a single family dwelling . Internal refurbishments and alterations to the elevations.  Changes to ground floor fenestration including reinstatement of original openings and replacement of windows and doors with triple glazed units. Installation of Air Source Heat Pump in rear garden.",
  "subdivision_of_building": "Flat 3 and 4 Ground Floor Frederick Building",
  "actual_completion_date": null,
  "lpa_app_no": "2024/0302",
  "decision": "Approved",
  "application_type_full": "Full planning permission",
